queues

Class Queue<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • queues.Queue<T>

  • public class Queue<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    class Queue which implements Iterable. Objects of type Queue manage items in a singly linked list where we can enqueue() from the front and dequeue() items from the end of the queue. Created by Fu on 29/1/2018.
